@startuml Authentication Flow

title Authentication Flow - Simplified

actor Admin
participant Browser
participant API
participant Database

== Login ==

Admin -> Browser: Enter credentials
Browser -> API: POST /login
API -> Database: Verify user
Database --> API: User data

alt Valid
    API --> Browser: JWT token + redirect
    Browser -> Admin: Dashboard
else Invalid
    API --> Browser: Error
    Browser -> Admin: Login error
end

== Access Protected Page ==

Admin -> Browser: Navigate
Browser -> API: Request + JWT
API -> API: Verify token & role

alt Authorized
    API -> Database: Get data
    Database --> API: Data
    API --> Browser: Page
    Browser -> Admin: Display
else Unauthorized
    API --> Browser: Redirect login
end

== Logout ==

Admin -> Browser: Click logout
Browser -> API: POST /logout
API -> Database: Invalidate token
API --> Browser: Redirect login

@enduml
